A Town Called Panic;;85;;81;;PG;;In this animated film, Cowboy (Stéphane Aubier) and Indian (Bruce Ellison) plan to construct a barbecue pit for the birthday of their friend, Horse (Vincent Patar). The delivery of an accidental purchase of 50 million bricks rather than the intended 50 destroys their house, and attempts to rebuild are foiled when their walls are continually stolen. Determined to track down the thieves, the trio travels to the center of the earth, where they discover the culprits are a group of mad scientists.;;Fantasy,Kids & family,Animation,Adventure,Comedy;;Stéphane Aubier,Vincent Patar;;2009;;Stéphane Aubier,Jeanne Balibar,Nicolas Buysse,Véronique Dumont,Bruce Ellison,Christine Grulois,Frédéric Jannin,Bouli Lanners,Christelle Mahy,Vincent Patar;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_town_called_panic